Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.99,0:02:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen's at it again!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.91,0:02:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.85,0:02:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.84,0:02:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit him back!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.25,0:02:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone stop him!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out{,} already!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.16,0:02:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.84,0:02:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.75,0:02:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.68,0:02:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, it was with a much older boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How in the world is he so strong?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.73,0:03:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And that temper of his... He's uncontrollable!{}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.57,0:03:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what he might do next.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.77,0:03:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even want to think about it.{The very thought sends chills down my spine.}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your face?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get in another fight?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.22,0:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They started it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They were talking about me behind my back.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,About Mom?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.74,0:03:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it's all a lie{ that she's sick}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.59,0:03:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They said she left because she hated me, \Nnot because she's sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's not a lie!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.41,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you behave,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom will get better soon and—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.19,0:03:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} a lie!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.19,0:03:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She got sick because she had me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.48,0:03:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder she doesn't want to see me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen! That's not true!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please listen to your father for one second.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.22,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just so full of energy that she can hardly bear to see you while she's so ill.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.57,0:04:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.13,0:04:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.58,0:04:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.72,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's got so many colors, and they're all moving around...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.21,0:05:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like it's alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.23,0:05:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's probably something else I'm not supposed to see...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}just like those.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I tell him I saw this, he'll get angry again.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.25,0:05:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone up there{,} in the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.29,0:06:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, is that an angel?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.35,0:06:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen, you...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk nonsense.{}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.76,0:06:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're imagining things.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.27,0:06:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's right there.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.03,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't see things like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.60,0:06:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Things like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.73,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,don't exist.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.13,0:06:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.01,0:06:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's weird. }It doesn't have any seams.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.30,0:06:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I read somewhere that angels wear clothes that don't have any seams.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.93,0:07:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}this is what she's been searching for.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Gen! Cut it out{,} already!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.32,0:07:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone go get a grown-up!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Gen, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten pretty big{ and strong}.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.21,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.28,0:07:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I met you once, back when you were just a baby.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to believe such a scrawny thing grew up like this.{..}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.61,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is }There something you want?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.56,0:07:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a strange robe at your home, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.63,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who brought you it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.55,0:08:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that your child is unwell as of late.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.03,0:08:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right to be worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.17,0:08:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am clothing him in a special robe.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.77,0:08:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Until he regains his strength,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,please leave this robe on him.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What robe?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.03,0:08:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing there.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen! You finally opened your eyes...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.19,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, would you consider just seeing how things go?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.60,0:09:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for thanks until after he's grown into a fine boy.{Keep this comment: NB: This is a good forum post on the use of "until" with "after": http://ell.stackexchange.com/questions/22389/whats-the-difference-between-until-and-until-after . In this sentence, Ginko is emphasizing that thanks aren't due now, but later. I therefore added the "after" as an intensifier, intended to emphasize the whole point of the line.}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.28,0:09:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how it went.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.64,0:09:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it may have worked a bit {\i1}too{\i0} well, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.85,0:09:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't control yourself when you get mad, can you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably in need of a bit of mushi-severing.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.61,0:09:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mushi"?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.35,0:09:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your affinity for mushi has become too strong.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.98,0:09:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a child with such a strong affinity,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.48,0:09:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you may have some difficulty \Ncontrolling yourself when you're mad.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.17,0:09:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want that, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.25,0:09:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then give me your hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.16,0:09:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do this, will I lose the ability to see her too?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.05,0:09:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But if you don't want that, \NI just won't go through with it all the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.01,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not coming out...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.11,0:10:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, typically, it should come out through your fingertips, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.04,0:10:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.60,0:10:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.93,0:10:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son's grown into a fine boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.51,0:10:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful that he's in good health,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but he can be so unruly.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.59,0:10:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I was willing to grasp at any chance of saving him...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.13,0:10:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but are you the one responsible \Nfor the way Gen is now?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, what exactly was it that you did to him?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.13,0:10:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked me not to tell you, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.75,0:11:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,back then, before I came to your house,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.21,0:11:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I met his mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.22,0:11:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who made that robe.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.04,0:11:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that robe?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful robe.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.82,0:11:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of curiosity, might I ask how you came to possess it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.47,0:11:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that kimono?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.53,0:12:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wove it myself, from thread I spun.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.90,0:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, I have no clue \Nwhat the thread is made out of.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.05,0:12:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Years ago, I suddenly became able to see things.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.03,0:12:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened after I gave birth \Nto my little boy and nearly died from it.{The first "It" should be clear from the dialogue, and although a little vaguer, the second "it" seems to clearly enough refer back to "giving birth."}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.65,0:12:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.59,0:12:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally awake!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.03,0:12:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is our baby...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.25,0:12:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A healthy baby boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.87,0:12:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hold him.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.68,0:12:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui, you've been asleep for several days.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.48,0:12:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So I took him back to our home.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.99,0:13:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring him to see you soon,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.01,0:13:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so until then, just focus on regaining \Nyour strength here at your family home.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.53,0:13:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.67,0:13:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Mom?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.53,0:13:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel as though I've been reborn.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.62,0:13:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The world looks like an entirely different place.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.68,0:13:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have the trees and the grass always been so radiant?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.27,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this thread?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.06,0:14:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whatever it is, it's beautiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.35,0:14:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this thread beautiful?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.98,0:14:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be getting a bit ahead of myself,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.12,0:14:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but I thought I could make \Nsomething special for Gen to wear{ on special occasions}.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.38,0:14:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thread?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.03,0:14:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, did you ever know you could harvest \Nsuch beautiful thread from the trees around here?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.86,0:14:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't strain yourself too much, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.64,0:15:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.03,0:15:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how I've wanted to meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems much better.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.96,0:15:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Yui doing lately?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.06,0:15:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are still some things that worry me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.53,0:15:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Every now and then, she says very strange things.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.20,0:15:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's glowing just like the trees.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.00,0:15:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He looks so wonderful.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.28,0:15:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.80,0:15:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, Gen's...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.23,0:15:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He suddenly went limp.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.23,0:15:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.56,0:16:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When I caressed him, \Nthis shining thread came out, and then...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.26,0:16:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.64,0:16:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get him to a doctor!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.20,0:16:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{You can}Just stay here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed as though it was shedding its skin.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.41,0:16:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the moment when I realized it was alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.77,0:17:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had never touched those threads...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.10,0:17:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My poor baby boy... What's going to happen to him?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unexpected.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.03,0:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Those threads of yours are \Nwhat we mushi-shi call the ether.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.14,0:17:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also what triggered your sudden ability \Nto see things you were unable to see before.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.59,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}But this is my first time hearing of someone able to spin it into \Nthread without using any medicine and using only their fingers.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.61,0:17:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens when you remove it from someone?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.04,0:17:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen to my son?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.93,0:17:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A fully grown child wouldn't be very affected,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.52,0:17:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but infants, on the other hand, need the ether to live.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.69,0:17:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Most are born with what they need.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.93,0:17:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if too much is extracted from them, they lose their vitality.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.35,0:17:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.05,0:18:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there something I can do to save him?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.08,0:18:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one way.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.17,0:18:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If we put this robe on him, he may live.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.87,0:18:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The results of which you well know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.67,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's grown into a very healthy boy, twice as strong as any his age.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.41,0:18:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he now has too {\i1}much{\i0} ether.{...rather than "too little," which is how much he had before.}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.06,0:18:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Under normal circumstances, \Nmushi-shi can extract it using medicine.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.68,0:18:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But that has no effect on him.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.31,0:18:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you may find all this a bit difficult to believe,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.62,0:18:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but perhaps you should talk to your son \Nand let him see his mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.31,0:18:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,With how things have progressed, she may \Nvery well be the only one who can extract his ether.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.97,0:18:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.74,0:18:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.67,0:18:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time, Mom didn't hate me after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.75,0:19:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see Mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.95,0:19:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.48,0:19:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had let you see her earlier...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.12,0:19:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been like this for almost two years.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.45,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like she's turned into an empty shell.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.81,0:19:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had forgiven her sooner...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She must have continued spinning the thread,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.84,0:19:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}probably in an attempt to make another robe.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.37,0:19:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's been exposed to so much ether \Nthat she's fallen under the mushi's influence.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.30,0:19:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should've paid more attention to her and not just her son.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.72,0:19:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Gen?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.85,0:20:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know her.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.85,0:20:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember her?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.36,0:20:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the angel who's been \Nwatching over me all this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.18,0:20:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That day, they took her back home with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.33,0:20:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After some time, vitality returned to her body.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.76,0:20:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.61,0:20:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Around that time,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.93,0:20:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the angel vanished.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.28,0:20:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I suddenly felt my body grow very light,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.54,0:20:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and before I knew it, I found myself watching him from the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.74,0:20:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy to see him growing so well.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.65,0:20:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Yui.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.84,0:21:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be. I'm sorry too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.05,0:21:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As we agreed,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.54,0:21:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take this robe.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.29,0:21:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's all you need?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.16,0:21:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more than enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.79,0:21:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A robe like this is exceedingly rare.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.86,0:21:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you still see the threads of light?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.40,0:21:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.92,0:21:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.42,0:21:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for the best for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.71,0:21:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But what shall I do about him?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.93,0:21:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.85,0:21:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll have to develop a more potent medicine...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.22,0:21:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.51,0:21:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm, guess there's no need for that medicine anymore.
